        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "BghWN",
          "x": 96,
          "y": 56,
          "width": 260,
          "height": 86,
          "fill": "#1E5E4B",
          "cornerRadius": 999,
          "layout": "none",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "qOth2",
              "x": 22,
              "y": 14,
              "fill": "#F5F0E8",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 220,
              "content": "CARD 02 /\nJACKQUANN + NIGEL",
              "lineHeight": 1.3,
              "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "Qgb6M",
          "x": 96,
          "y": 160,
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 740,
          "content": "Neither boy asked for punishment",
          "lineHeight": 0.96,
          "fontFamily": "Playfair Display",
          "fontSize": 68,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "tI7mQ",
          "x": 96,
          "y": 310,
          "fill": "#4F463F",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 710,
          "content": "Both boys live in Alice Springs. Neither has been asked what they need. When asked, Jackquann told politicians one word: \"Programs.\" Nigel said he wants to be a footy player and knows he needs to go to school every day to get there.\n\nBoth have been to detention. Both named family as the thing detention takes away. Oonchiumpa picks them up, takes them to school, and gives them someone to walk with.",
          "lineHeight": 1.26,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 24,
          "fontWeight": "500"
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "yVjOp",
          "x": 96,
          "y": 740,
          "width": 710,
          "height": 154,
          "fill": "#E3F2EB",
          "cornerRadius": 28,
          "stroke": {
            "thickness": 2,
            "fill": "#9FCFBD"
          },
          "layout": "none",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "f2iCe",
              "x": 28,
              "y": 26,
              "fill": "#1E5E4B",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 654,
              "content": "\"Sometime they feel bored. They got nothing to do at home.\" - Nigel, on why young people steal cars",
              "lineHeight": 1.24,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 24,
              "fontWeight": "600"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "PxADK",
          "x": 956,
          "y": 56,
          "width": 468,
          "height": 938,
          "fill": "#E8F4EF",
