          "layout": "none",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "XMvhI",
              "x": 22,
              "y": 18,
              "fill": "#FFF6F2",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 206,
              "content": "CARD 05 / LAQUISHA",
              "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
              "fontSize": 18,
              "fontWeight": "700"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "UBtTv",
          "x": 96,
          "y": 150,
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 740,
          "content": "Laquisha named the structure plainly",
          "lineHeight": 0.96,
          "fontFamily": "Playfair Display",
          "fontSize": 68,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "LwNAw",
          "x": 96,
          "y": 332,
          "fill": "#4F463F",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": 710,
          "content": "Laquisha lives with her auntie. She is 16, goes to St Joseph's. She has been to Darwin youth detention, 1,500km from home. Twelve-minute phone calls. Two-hour waits between calls. No family there. Lockdown at 6:30 every night.\n\nWhen asked why young people get in trouble, she answered in one word: \"Oppression.\" She wants her driver's licence. She wants to travel. Court is scary because you don't know whether you are getting out or not, and your family is sitting there watching.",
          "lineHeight": 1.26,
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 22,
          "fontWeight": "500"
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "Ift9Z",
          "x": 96,
          "y": 740,
          "width": 710,
          "height": 176,
          "fill": "#FFF1EC",
          "cornerRadius": 28,
          "layout": "none",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "pbsfI",
              "x": 0,
              "y": 0,
              "width": 12,
              "height": 176,
              "fill": "#C14E33"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "zvj0M",
              "x": 36,
              "y": 34,
              "fill": "#7A3424",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": 654,
              "content": "\"It would've been better hanging around with family instead of sitting in your cell by yourself. Just 12 minute calls.\" - Laquisha",
              "lineHeight": 1.24,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 24,
              "fontWeight": "600"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
